                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout>
                           <p>Columns: 3;
                                                  ruled lines: 29;
                                                  written lines: 28; Folios 2-5 and 274 added in the 18th century. Numbers, Song of Songs and Ecclesisates commence a new leaf. Initial words of Genesis, Song of Songs and Haftarot written in larger letters. Beginnings of pericopes in the Pentateuch marked in the margin by ornamented פ or פר. </p>
                        </layout>
